  "reference_number": "IRN0136",
  "remarks": "\nMohammad KARAMI is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 as in his former role as the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC) Ground Forces Commander for the Quds Operational Base, he is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting serious human rights violations in Iran through the repression of recent protests in Iran, leading to violations of the right of life and violations of the right to freedom of expression and peaceful assembly.",
